(751, 1, '2014-01-14 11:15:56', '2014-01-14 11:15:56', 'The problem: In the ten year period between 2001 and 2011 U.S. health care spending nearly doubled, climbing from $1.5 trillion to $2.7 trillion. Even though we‚Äôre spending so much as a nation, we rank 26th in the world for life expectancy. Projections for chronic diseases, the aging population, costs of hospital readmissions and physician shortage only make the future more challenging.\r\n\r\nTeleHealth365 was founded to tackle these four problems, to empower people to take responsibility through preventive measures, and to make health care affordable and accessible in the comfort and convenience of their own home. We do this by:\r\n\r\nEmpowering health care providers and their patients to connect anytime, anywhere, on any device.\r\n\r\nEmpowering people to manage and improve all aspects of their personal health.\r\n\r\nTelehealth365 OmniPresence‚Ñ¢ connects patients with clinical healthcare providers anywhere around the world. Our mission is to provide healthcare anytime, anywhere so that patients can receive the treatment they need and get well sooner. We provide affordable, innovative and secure video conferencing for the patient-physician encounter. \r\nThe video uses the latest technology and provides clear high definition images. We provide a total solution for the patient-physician encounter, including the sharing of health information between primary care physicians and specialists.\r\n\r\nTeleHealth365 OmniCare‚Ñ¢ gives physicians health data regarding their patients. We believe that by empowering people to monitor their health with the next generation of smart wearable devices, they can provide healthcare workers with ‚ÄúIntelligent‚Äù data in real time. Omnicare improves people‚Äôs wellness and lowers the cost of health care. When people monitor their conditions at home, they are more vigilant about their health and more willing to follow their physician‚Äôs and health coach‚Äôs recommendations.', 'Our Mission', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'our-mission', '', '', '2015-02-10 14:14:02', '2015-02-10 14:14:02', '', 0, 'https://www.telehealth365.com/?page_id=751', 0, 'page', '', 0),
