(853, 1, '2014-02-25 04:46:02', '2014-02-25 04:46:02', '<strong>OmniReach ‚Äì a video solution for global users.</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://burfee.mmware.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Mmware_Video_10.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-852 alignright" alt="Mmware_Video_10" src="http://burfee.mmware.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Mmware_Video_10.jpg" width="204" height="204" /></a>Mmware‚Äôs OmniReach is amazingly easy to deploy, making instant face-to-face collaboration possible with anyone, anywhere. No software to download or install. Business-class performance in HD video\r\n\r\nMmware‚Äôs OmniReach video collaboration solution enables businesses to collaborate with other businesses ‚Äì or individuals ‚Äì easily and securely, on any mobile device, tablet, or laptop. It‚Äôs high quality, reliable and secure.\r\n\r\nAffordable and scalable: Grows with you as your business grows. No expensive equipment to purchase. Uses what you already have.\r\n\r\n<strong>No complicated software to install. Easy to use.</strong>\r\n\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†High-quality B2B and B2C video collaboration platform.\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†Simple click-to-guest convenience invites anyone by sending a URL link in an IM, email, or calendar invitation\r\n\r\n<strong>OmniReach enables video collaboration for:</strong>\r\n\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†Distance learning\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†Telemedicine\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†Manufacturing\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†Customer Services\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†Business Continuity\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†Law &amp; Order\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†Home security\r\n‚Ä¢¬†¬† ¬†Federal, State, and local government.', 'Video Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '819-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-25 04:46:02', '2014-02-25 04:46:02', '', 819, 'http://burfee.mmware.com/819-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
