(2555, 1, '2016-02-28 18:37:44', '2016-02-28 18:37:44', '<strong>Leadership Team</strong>\r\n<h3 style="color: #141414;"><strong>Vijay Sharma</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>Founder</strong>\r\n\r\nVijay Sharma is passionate about creating innovation that makes a positive difference in the world. He brings over 25 years of experience in developing Real-Time Communication &amp; Collaboration platforms for Fortune 500 companies and startups. He has served as CTO, VP and Director of Engineering for public listed and startup companies. His products have generated Billions of dollars in sales and helped millions of businesses improve their communications with customers.\r\n\r\nIn 2003, he founded Aelix Systems Inc, which was acquired by eOn Communications in 2005. Vijay has held engineering and senior management positions with Avaya Inc, eOn Communications, Aelix Systems Inc, Cidco Communications, Qorus, IPC Systems, Philips Business Systems, Plessey Office Systems and British Aerospace.\r\n<h3 style="color: #141414;"><strong>Dele Olajide</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>Co-Founder</strong>\r\n\r\nDele Olajide has over 25 years of experience in designing and developing collaboration and communication solutions. He is a systems integration expert and has contributed thousands of lines of code to open source technologies as well as authoring open standards. He has held engineering and consultant positions with BT Global Services, Infosys, Voxeo, Binteo and many other companies.\r\n<h3 style="color: #141414;"><strong>Usha Sharma</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>Co-Founder</strong>\r\n\r\nUsha Sharma is a social entrepreneur, author and catalyst for positive change. She is a graduate of the University of Virginia in brain and behavior sciences.\r\nUsha serves as a vision mentor and coach for World Pulse, an action media network that lifts the voices of grassroots leaders from 190 countries to accelerate their impact in the world. Her clients have addressed the United Nations, created schools in the developing world, spread unity in diversity, and spearheaded companies such as Disney.\r\n<h3 style="color: #141414;"><strong>Geoff Murphy</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>Vice President of Business Development</strong>\r\n\r\nGeoff Murphy has 20 plus years of experience in telecommunications hardware and software. He has been responsible for building sales channels in North America. During his tenure with Comdial and eOn Communications, he signed over 200 plus dealers in US and Globally.\r\n<h3 style="color: #141414;"><strong>Yash Arora</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>Engineering, India</strong>\r\n\r\nYash Arora has over 14 years of experience developing leading edge web and mobile applications. In addition to leading engineering teams in India, he is also a hands-on technical contributor\r\n<h3 style="color: #141414;"><strong>Engineering Teams</strong></h3>\r\nChandigarh, India\r\nLondon, UK\r\nSan Jose, USA.\r\n<h3 style="color: #141414;"><strong>International</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>South East Asia & Middle East</strong>', 'Company', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-28 18:37:44', '2016-02-28 18:37:44', '', 18, 'https://www.telehealth365.com/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
